  "mainClass": "flex-1 flex bg-surface-container-low overflow-hidden min-h-0",
  "mainHtml": "<aside class=\"history-panel flex flex-col h-full min-h-0 bg-surface border-r border-outline-variant shrink-0\" id=\"historyPanel\">\n<div class=\"history-head-wrap p-4 border-b border-outline-variant\">\n<div class=\"history-head flex items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n<div class=\"history-brand flex items-center gap-3 min-w-0\">\n<div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary-container text-primary flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]\">history</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"history-copy min-w-0\">\n<p class=\"text-label-md font-bold text-on-surface\">Conversation History</p>\n<p class=\"text-label-sm text-secondary truncate\">Text-to-Model Task History</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<button class=\"p-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-surface-container-low transition-colors shrink-0\" id=\"historyToggle\" type=\"button\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]\">chevron_left</span>\n</button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"history-search mt-4 relative\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-[18px] text-on-surface-variant\">search</span>\n<input class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low py-2 pl-10 pr-3 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" placeholder=\"Search task history\" type=\"text\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"history-list flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-4 space-y-3 chat-scroll\">\n<button class=\"history-item is-current w-full rounded-2xl border border-primary/20 bg-primary/5 p-3 text-left transition-colors hover:bg-primary/10\" title=\"Engine Bracket Request Task\" type=\"button\">\n<div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n<div class=\"history-item-icon mt-0.5 w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary text-on-primary flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]\">description</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"history-item-copy min-w-0\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-2\">\n<span class=\"text-body-sm font-bold text-on-surface truncate\">Engine Bracket Request</span>\n<span class=\"text-[10px] text-on-surface-variant shrink-0\">10:42</span>\n</div>\n<p class=\"mt-1 text-[11px] text-on-surface-variant line-clamp-2\">V6 assembly bracket, lightweight, 45kg static load, safety factor 2.0, now in parameter confirmation.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</button>\n<button class=\"history-item w-full rounded-2xl border border-transparent bg-surface-container-low p-3 text-left transition-colors hover:border-outline-variant hover:bg-surface-container\" title=\"Pump Housing Optimization Task\" type=\"button\">\n<div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n<div class=\"history-item-icon mt-0.5 w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-surface-container-high text-on-surface flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]\">deployed_code</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"history-item-copy min-w-0\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-2\">\n<span class=\"text-body-sm font-bold text-on-surface truncate\">Pump Housing Optimization</span>\n<span class=\"text-[10px] text-on-surface-variant shrink-0\">Yesterday</span>\n</div>\n<p class=\"mt-1 text-[11px] text-on-surface-variant line-clamp-2\">Keep the exterior profile, allow optimization of internal ribs, and suit CNC machining.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</button>\n<button class=\"history-item w-full rounded-2xl border border-transparent bg-surface-container-lowest p-3 text-left transition-colors hover:border-outline-variant hover:bg-surface-container-low\" title=\"Robot Arm Structure Task\" type=\"button\">\n<div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n<div class=\"history-item-icon mt-0.5 w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-surface-container text-on-surface flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]\">smart_toy</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"history-item-copy min-w-0\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-2\">\n<span class=\"text-body-sm font-bold text-on-surface truncate\">Robot Arm Structure</span>\n<span class=\"text-[10px] text-on-surface-variant shrink-0\">Jul 03</span>\n</div>\n<p class=\"mt-1 text-[11px] text-on-surface-variant line-clamp-2\">The text request has been transferred for manual review. Waiting for assembly relationships and mating hole details.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"history-footer p-4 border-t border-outline-variant\">\n<button class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-4 py-2 text-[12px] font-bold text-primary hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors\" type=\"button\">\nView All History\n</button>\n</div>\n</aside><section class=\"flex-1 flex flex-col min-w-0 min-h-0 h-full p-6 relative\">\n<div class=\"relative flex-1 flex flex-col bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-outline-variant overflow-hidden min-h-0\">\n<div class=\"px-6 py-4 border-b border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-lowest flex-shrink-0\">\n<div class=\"flex w-fit p-1 bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl\">\n<a class=\"px-6 py-2 font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface-variant hover:text-on-surface transition-colors\" href=\"/ai/smart-quote\">Intelligent Quoting</a>\n<a class=\"px-6 py-2 font-label-md text-label-md bg-surface-container-lowest text-primary font-bold shadow-sm rounded-lg\" href=\"/ai/text-to-3d\">Text to Model</a>\n<a class=\"px-6 py-2 font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface-variant hover:text-on-surface transition-colors\" href=\"/ai/image-to-3d\">Image to Model</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex-1 min-h-0 overflow-y-auto p-6 pb-56 space-y-8 chat-scroll\">\n<div class=\"flex flex-col items-end\">\n<div class=\"bg-primary text-on-primary p-4 rounded-2xl rounded-tr-none max-w-lg shadow-md\">\n<p class=\"text-body-sm\">Please generate a lightweight aluminum engine bracket for a V6 assembly. It needs to support a 45kg static load with a safety factor of 2.0 and be optimized for CNC milling.</p>\n</div>\n<span class=\"text-[10px] text-on-surface-variant mt-1 px-2\">10:42 AM</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex flex-col items-start\">\n<div class=\"flex gap-3 max-w-[calc(100%-2rem)]\">\n<div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary-container flex items-center justify-center text-primary shrink-0\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\" style=\"font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;\">auto_awesome</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"space-y-4 min-w-0\">\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-high p-4 rounded-2xl rounded-tl-none shadow-sm border border-outline-variant\">\n<p class=\"text-body-sm text-on-surface\">I understand your text request. To avoid AI generating a model that does not match manufacturing requirements, I will first collect dimensions, tolerances, material, process, assembly, and output format, then generate the model and sync the quote and order information on the right.</p>\n<div class=\"mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2\">\n<button class=\"rounded-xl bg-primary px-4 py-2 text-[12px] font-bold text-on-primary hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity\" data-scroll-wizard=\"\" type=\"button\">Start Parameter Collection</button>\n<button class=\"rounded-xl border border-primary/20 bg-primary/5 px-4 py-2 text-[12px] font-bold text-primary hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors\" data-human-support=\"\" type=\"button\">Transfer to Manual Assistance</button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden rounded-2xl border border-[#f6c47a] bg-[#fff7eb] p-4 shadow-sm\" id=\"humanSupportCard\">\n<div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n<div class=\"mt-0.5 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[#ffedd5] text-[#c2410c] flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]\">support_agent</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"min-w-0\">\n<p class=\"text-body-sm font-bold text-on-surface\">Manual review service is ready</p>\n<p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] text-on-surface-variant\">If AI understanding of the text request is unstable、If the structure is too complex or you want an engineer to confirm key conditions first，You can transfer directly to the manual team。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-lowest shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n<div class=\"p-4 border-b border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low\">\n<div class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<div>\n<p class=\"text-body-sm font-bold text-on-surface\">Recommended Text Prompt Example</p>\n<p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] text-on-surface-variant\">You can describe your part like the example below. AI will understand it faster and enter parameter collection more smoothly.</p>\n</div>\n<span class=\"rounded-full bg-primary/10 px-3 py-1 text-[10px] font-bold text-primary\">Sample</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"p-4 bg-surface-container-lowest\">\n<div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-surface-container-low p-4 text-[12px] text-on-surface leading-6\">\nPlease generate a lightweight bracket for a V6 engine assembly. Overall dimensions are approximately 320 x 110 x 96 mm. Prefer Aluminum 6061-T6 with a 5-axis CNC machining process. It needs to support a 45kg static load with a safety factor of 2.0. The four mounting holes must be coaxial, the outer profile should remain compact, and the internal structure can be optimized for weight reduction. Standard tolerance is ±0.05 mm. Output a STEP file. Initial batch: 20 pcs. Lead time: 10 days.\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-lowest shadow-sm overflow-hidden\" id=\"parameterWizard\">\n<div class=\"px-5 py-4 border-b border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low\">\n<div class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<div>\n<p class=\"text-body-sm font-bold text-on-surface\">Model Generation Parameter Collection</p>\n<p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] text-on-surface-variant\">Based on your text request, the system will collect manufacturing parameters step by step before generating the model.</p>\n</div>\n<span class=\"rounded-full bg-primary/10 px-3 py-1 text-[10px] font-bold text-primary\" id=\"stepCounter\">Step 1 / 5</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2\">\n<button class=\"step-trigger is-active rounded-xl bg-surface-container px-3 py-2 text-[12px] text-on-surface-variant transition-colors\" data-step-trigger=\"0\" type=\"button\">1. Size &amp; Tolerance</button>\n<button class=\"step-trigger rounded-xl bg-surface-container px-3 py-2 text-[12px] text-on-surface-variant transition-colors\" data-step-trigger=\"1\" type=\"button\">2. Material &amp; Process</button>\n<button class=\"step-trigger rounded-xl bg-surface-container px-3 py-2 text-[12px] text-on-surface-variant transition-colors\" data-step-trigger=\"2\" type=\"button\">3. Output &amp; AI</button>\n<button class=\"step-trigger rounded-xl bg-surface-container px-3 py-2 text-[12px] text-on-surface-variant transition-colors\" data-step-trigger=\"3\" type=\"button\">4. Manufacturing Constraints</button>\n<button class=\"step-trigger rounded-xl bg-surface-container px-3 py-2 text-[12px] text-on-surface-variant transition-colors\" data-step-trigger=\"4\" type=\"button\">5. Review &amp; Confirm</button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"p-5\">\n<div class=\"space-y-6\" data-step-panel=\"0\">\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">Overall Length</span><input class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" placeholder=\"e.g. 320\" type=\"number\" value=\"320\"/></label>\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">Overall Width</span><input class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" placeholder=\"e.g. 110\" type=\"number\" value=\"110\"/></label>\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">Overall Height</span><input class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" placeholder=\"e.g. 96\" type=\"number\" value=\"96\"/></label>\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">Unit</span><select class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\"><option selected=\"\">mm</option><option>cm</option><option>inch</option></select></label>\n</div>\n<label class=\"flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-4 py-3 text-body-sm text-on-surface\"><input checked=\"\" class=\"h-4 w-4 rounded border-outline text-primary focus:ring-primary\" type=\"checkbox\"/>Allow AI to estimate missing dimensions</label>\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">Tolerance / Precision Requirement</span><select class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" id=\"toleranceSelect\"><option>Standard ±0.1 mm</option><option selected=\"\">Standard ±0.05 mm</option><option>Precision ±0.02 mm (2D drawing required)</option><option>Ultra Precision ±0.01 mm (2D drawing required)</option></select></label>\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">Manufacturable</span><select class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\"><option selected=\"\">AI Manufacturability Prediction</option><option>Clearly manufacturable</option><option>Not sure yet, manual review required</option></select></label>\n</div>\n<p class=\"rounded-xl bg-emerald-50 px-4 py-3 text-[12px] text-emerald-700\" id=\"toleranceHelper\">This is a standard tolerance level and no additional 2D drawing is required.</p>\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">Minimum Wall Thickness</span><input class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" placeholder=\"e.g. 3.0 mm\" type=\"text\" value=\"3.0 mm\"/></label>\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">Hole Depth</span><input class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" placeholder=\"e.g. 28 mm\" type=\"text\" value=\"28 mm\"/></label>\n</div>\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-3\">\n<label class=\"flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-4 py-3 text-[12px] text-on-surface\"><input checked=\"\" class=\"h-4 w-4 rounded border-outline text-primary focus:ring-primary\" type=\"checkbox\"/>AI Auto Wall Thickness Detection</label>\n<label class=\"flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-4 py-3 text-[12px] text-on-surface\"><input checked=\"\" class=\"h-4 w-4 rounded border-outline text-primary focus:ring-primary\" type=\"checkbox\"/>Allow wall-thickness optimization</label>\n</div>\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">Fit Relationship</span><textarea class=\"min-h-[84px] w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" placeholder=\"e.g. the four holes must be coaxial and fit with the outer bearing race\">The four mounting holes must be coaxial and fit with the outer bearing race.</textarea></label>\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">Part Name</span><input class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" id=\"partNameInput\" type=\"text\" value=\"Engine Bracket\"/></label>\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">Part Function</span><input class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" type=\"text\" value=\"Engine assembly mounting and load support\"/></label>\n<label class=\"block col-span-2\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">Industry</span><select class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\"><option selected=\"\">Automotive Components</option><option>General Machinery</option><option>Robotics</option><option>Medical Devices</option><option>Consumer Electronics</option><option>Aerospace</option><option>Other</option></select></label>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden space-y-6\" data-step-panel=\"1\">\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">Material</span><select class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" id=\"materialSelect\"><option>Aluminum 7075-T6</option><option selected=\"\">Aluminum 6061-T6</option><option>Stainless Steel 304</option><option>Stainless Steel 316L</option><option>ABS Plastic</option><option>PC Polycarbonate</option><option>PEEK</option><option>Other</option><option>AI-Recommended Material</option></select></label>\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">Manufacturing Process</span><select class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" id=\"processSelect\"><option>CNC Machining</option><option>Sheet Metal</option><option>3D Printing</option><option>Injection Molding</option><option>Casting</option><option>Die Casting</option><option>Laser Cutting</option><option>Turning</option><option>Milling</option><option selected=\"\">5-Axis Machining</option><option>AI Auto Recommendation</option></select></label>\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">Surface Finish</span><select class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" id=\"surfaceSelect\"><option>No Finish</option><option>Sandblasting</option><option selected=\"\">Anodizing</option><option>Black Oxide</option><option>Painting</option><option>Brushing</option><option>Polishing</option><option>Electroplating</option><option>Zinc Plating</option><option>Nickel Plating</option><option>Powder Coating</option><option>AI Recommended</option></select></label>\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">AI Structural Optimization</span><select class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" id=\"structureSelect\"><option>No Modification</option><option>Optimization Allowed</option><option selected=\"\">Maximize Manufacturability</option><option>Maximize text fidelity</option></select></label>\n</div>\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">Generation Goal</span><select class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" id=\"goalSelect\"><option>Visual Match</option><option selected=\"\">Manufacturability First</option><option>Lowest Cost</option><option>Highest Strength</option><option>Lowest Weight</option><option>AI Balanced</option></select></label>\n<div>\n<span class=\"mb-3 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">Holes &amp; Threads</span>\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-[12px]\">\n<label class=\"flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2\"><input checked=\"\" class=\"h-4 w-4 rounded border-outline text-primary focus:ring-primary\" type=\"checkbox\"/>Round Holes</label>\n<label class=\"flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2\"><input checked=\"\" class=\"h-4 w-4 rounded border-outline text-primary focus:ring-primary\" type=\"checkbox\"/>Threaded Holes</label>\n<label class=\"flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2\"><input class=\"h-4 w-4 rounded border-outline text-primary focus:ring-primary\" type=\"checkbox\"/>Countersunk Holes</label>\n<label class=\"flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2\"><input class=\"h-4 w-4 rounded border-outline text-primary focus:ring-primary\" type=\"checkbox\"/>Counterbored Holes</label>\n<label class=\"flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2\"><input checked=\"\" class=\"h-4 w-4 rounded border-outline text-primary focus:ring-primary\" type=\"checkbox\"/>Locating Holes</label>\n<label class=\"flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2\"><input class=\"h-4 w-4 rounded border-outline text-primary focus:ring-primary\" type=\"checkbox\"/>Keyways</label>\n<label class=\"flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2\"><input checked=\"\" class=\"h-4 w-4 rounded border-outline text-primary focus:ring-primary\" type=\"checkbox\"/>Chamfers</label>\n<label class=\"flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2\"><input checked=\"\" class=\"h-4 w-4 rounded border-outline text-primary focus:ring-primary\" type=\"checkbox\"/>Fillets</label>\n<label class=\"flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2\"><input checked=\"\" class=\"h-4 w-4 rounded border-outline text-primary focus:ring-primary\" type=\"checkbox\"/>AI Recognition</label>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden space-y-6\" data-step-panel=\"2\">\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">Output Format</span><select class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" id=\"outputFormatSelect\"><option selected=\"\">STEP</option><option>STP</option><option>IGES</option><option>OBJ</option><option>STL</option><option>Parasolid</option><option>SolidWorks</option><option>Fusion360</option></select></label>\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">AI Interpretation Mode</span><select class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" id=\"understandingSelect\"><option>Appearance Modeling</option><option>Engineering Modeling</option><option>Manufacturable Modeling</option><option selected=\"\">CNC Machining Modeling</option><option>3D Printing Modeling</option><option>AI Auto Decision (Recommended)</option></select></label>\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">AI Modeling Precision</span><select class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\"><option>Fast</option><option selected=\"\">Standard</option><option>High Precision</option><option>Industrial Grade</option></select></label>\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">Surface Fitting</span><select class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\"><option>Low</option><option selected=\"\">Medium</option><option>High</option></select></label>\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">Feature Preservation</span><select class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\"><option>Conservative</option><option selected=\"\">Balanced</option><option>Fully Preserve</option></select></label>\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">AI Auto Surface Patch</span><select class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\"><option selected=\"\">Enabled</option><option>Disabled</option></select></label>\n<label class=\"block col-span-2\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">AI Auto Model Repair</span><select class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\"><option selected=\"\">Enabled</option><option>Disabled</option></select></label>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden space-y-6\" data-step-